  "title": "Driver cum Plant Nurturer x 2 | Bedok & Choa Chu Kang !!",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Position: Driver cum Plant Nurturer x 2 </strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Industry: Provider of Indoor Plant & Maintenance Services For Corporate</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>2 Headcount Required [ Tengah / Choa Chu Kang ] x 1 / Bedok x 1</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $2,300 - $2,400 + OT</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><p><u><em><strong>Class 3 driving license, driving 10 footer lorry, manual type, vehicle unable to drive back, pick up daily in office.</strong></em></u><br /><u><em><strong>One station in Bedok office, another headcount station in Choa Chu Kang office !!</strong></em></u></p></li><li><p>Min 2 years of driving experience is required for this role</p></li></ol><p>Job Scopes:</p><ul><li><p>Adhere to assigned schedule and ensure work tasks are completed on time.</p></li><li><p>Transporting workers and goods to sites.</p></li><li><p>Collecting and disposing of rubbish from work sites.</p></li><li><p>Safely securing heavy loads and large goods for transport.</p></li><li><p>Organizing the most efficient route from pickup point to drop off point.</p></li><li><p>Organizing multiple drop-offs and deliveries in each working day.</p></li><li><p>Support landscape and hydroculture maintenance work.</p></li><li><p>Upkeep assigned company vehicle: routine checking of engine; & general cleanliness.</p></li><li><p>Ensuring vehicles are mechanically sound and legally roadworthy.</p></li><li><p>Immediately complete and submit accident reports (e.g., injuries) to your manager.</p></li><li><p>Supervising and assisting with the loading and unloading of deliveries into the lorry.</p></li><li><p>Complying with all LTA and in-house regulations and rule.</p></li><li><p>Other duties and responsibilities as assigned.</p></li></ul><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
